data.text:
Each year, WSU students apply to Physical Therapy programs across the nation. The data below represents the students who completed their prerequisite coursework at WSU and matriculated into a program in the fall of 2022

Important Notes:

WSU had 44 verified applicants with 31 total offers. This is a 70% percentage rate.

Successful WSU candidates = overall GPA 3.52, science GPA 3.24

Successful national averages = overal GPA 3.55, science GPA 3.34

Data pulled from the Universal Advisors Portal (PTCAS) on 7/12/2023
